body_html:
Hey,

Thank you for your response, I really appreciate it. I was able to resolve
that issue. However, while running the program I am getting another error
"TypeError: Signature mismatch. Keys must be dtype <dtype: 'string'>, got
dtype:'int64'"

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/39730528/typeerror-signature-mismatch-keys-must-be-dtype-dtype-string-got-dtype

Did you receive this error during your execution or do you know what could
be the reason for it?

Warm Regards,
Vasanti Mahajan

On Sat, Sep 24, 2016 at 3:06 PM, simon789 notifications@github.com wrote:

since my previous comment, I have changed the classification/label data
from a number (1/0) to string data (win/lose) and this has resolved this
problem
